Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models

Class UserEntity

java.lang.Object
com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models.UserEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
@Entity public class UserEntity extends Object implements org.springframework.security.core.userdetails.UserDetails
The database entity for a User. This entity contains all non-Spring information we need about a user.
